N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1ยง 1.5 - Vitamin D content to be determined in approved laboratories

State Regulations

The vitamin D level of milk shall be ascertained in
laboratories approved in writing for such purpose by the
commissioner. Notes
